data.description: Price enhancement! Highly Sought After West Oak Hills Home! This home offer 3 bedroom, 2 bath and 2 car garage on a little over 2 acres.  Paved roads lead up to a hill top home with 360 view. This single story home offers a master suite with duel sinks and walk in shower.  The Kitchen has a nook with bar area that opens to cozy family room with a wood burning rock fire place. Step outside to a covered patio and imagine sitting on your side deck sipping your coffee overlooking a tranquil fish pond enjoying your private surroundings with a view of the mountains and hills. Also included are two out buildings.  One is currently used as a workshop, to work on your favorite hobbies and projects, and the other for extra storage or private retreat. Enjoy Rural living at its best with close access  to freeway, shopping, restaurants and entertainment.
